text: Olga Umaralieva (born February 5, 1988) is an Uzbekistani sprint canoeist. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's K-1 200 metres event but did not advance past the heats. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Uzbekistani female canoeists Category:Olympic canoeists of Uzbekistan Category:Canoeists at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Canoeists at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Canoeists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games competitors for Uzbekistan
